<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="A" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Adversary" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Adversary,</orth> 1) opponent, antagonist; in a suit at law: <bibl n="shak. mv 4.1" default="NO" valid="yes">Merch. IV, 1, 4</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. shr 1.2.278" default="NO" valid="yes">Shr. I, 2, 278</bibl>. In single combat: <bibl n="shak. r2 1.3" default="NO" valid="yes">R2 I, 3, 92</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h6 5.5" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A V, 5, 33</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lr 5.3" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. V, 3, 123</bibl>.<lb />2) enemy: <bibl n="shak. aww 3.6.28" default="NO" valid="yes">Alls III, 6, 28</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. aww 4.1.17" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 1, 17</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r2 1.1.101" default="NO" valid="yes">R2 I, 1, 101</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h4 3.2.83" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A III, 2, 83</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h4 5.5.31" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 5, 31</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 1.1.11" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 I, 1, 11</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 1.3.123" default="NO" valid="yes">I, 3, 123</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 3.1.182" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 1, 182</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 4.4.4" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 4, 4</bibl> (Ff <emph>enemies</emph>). <bibl n="shak. r3 5.3.112" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 3, 112</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 5.3.112" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 3, 112</bibl> <bibl n="shak. cor 4.3.45" default="NO" valid="yes">Cor. IV, 3, 45</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. rom 1.1.113" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. I, 1, 113</bibl>.
<lb />Misapplied by Mrs Quickly: <bibl n="shak. wiv 2.3.98" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. II, 3, 98</bibl>. Fluellen pronounces <cit><quote>athversary:</quote> <bibl n="shak. h5 3.2.65" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 III, 2, 65</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. h5 3.6.98" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 6, 98</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h5 3.6.98" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 6, 98</bibl>
